{"tid":1131660,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好想知我同佢有冇機會:(有冇人可以比下建議我","createTime":"2019-04-29T19:59:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T18:19:17.000Z","uid":188871,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3be58b104a507976c243d5216f7a3dabe5f08d36","tid":1131660,"uid":188871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T19:59:45.000Z","msg":"上年年尾因工作識到一個男仔，<br />\n一開始大家傾計內容都圍繞住工作，<br />\n而見面都只係交換器材，都係關於工作。<br />\n佢算係半公眾人物，而我就係普通打工女，<br />\n本來都冇諗過會同佢有啲咩交接。<br />\n<br />\n但係由今年年頭開始，大家見面見多左，<br />\n我同佢都因為工作成日香港台灣兩地走，<br />\n每次我飛去台灣或者佢返嚟香港都會見面食餐飯，<br />\n傾計內容由工作變成會傾大家近況，<br />\n仲有試過傾感情問題(由相識到現時大家都單身)<br />\n仲有好多野都會問對方意見咁樣。<br />\n<br />\n我同佢最大嘅轉捩點應該就係上個月同佢做完一單job之後佢病左，我好擔心佢，<br />\n我有帶d藥上去佢屋企，但放低就走左，<br />\n第二日佢就又要返台灣工作，我就心掛掛咁，<br />\n之後我就開始覺得自己有少少奶左野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講多啲我同佢嘅details先<br />\n佢：30歲，月入廿萬，都算靚仔，出街未必有人識但都有啲名氣，工作太忙，個人冇乜朋友，但因工作會成日同d小模接觸，不煙不酒<br />\n我：23歲，月入兩萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />普通女仔樣，唔係小模樣，都係不煙不酒<br />\n<br />\n有一次同佢出去食飯佢仲話等我生日會送花俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知係吹水定認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家日日都好掛住佢但又唔敢搵佢，怕佢覺得我煩，我驚最後連朋友都冇得做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea1080c799992121bfe813b79fa71ca07c004efd","tid":1131660,"uid":3325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T20:04:35.000Z","msg":"月入廿萬老閪都主動溝佢啦戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aa43c19a3acd44efba6429eb6d6c40004ce0155","tid":1131660,"uid":188871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea1080c799992121bfe813b79fa71ca07c004efd","tid":1131660,"uid":3325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T20:04:35.000Z","msg":"月入廿萬老閪都主動溝佢啦戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T20:06:27.000Z","msg":"但驚講左就連朋友都冇得做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b9f0f55447e47c8c0ed459574995859c7789712","tid":1131660,"uid":3325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4aa43c19a3acd44efba6429eb6d6c40004ce0155","tid":1131660,"uid":188871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea1080c799992121bfe813b79fa71ca07c004efd","tid":1131660,"uid":3325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T20:04:35.000Z","msg":"月入廿萬老閪都主動溝佢啦戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T20:06:27.000Z","msg":"但驚講左就連朋友都冇得做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T20:11:16.000Z","msg":"唔試咪做一世朋友"},{"pid":"179ad31babbe118e63c11607885bafa639260849","tid":1131660,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T23:11:48.000Z","msg":"Ptgf"},{"pid":"547c7782f829e1811754c0c6f893bc7c97a7dd28","tid":1131660,"uid":247934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T00:20:56.000Z","msg":"求財啫 開去經濟台好似合理d啊"},{"pid":"51b9b41da81025cd7b7ee0ebe4854686a421b127","tid":1131660,"uid":251421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T18:12:16.000Z","msg":"條友係咪對你有興趣先<br />\n試下努力啲比佢知你先係關心佢嘅人囉"},{"pid":"c01c62643f845982f40de830ef0bed987f943da1","tid":1131660,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T18:13:50.000Z","msg":"有無雙方八字？幫你算下"},{"pid":"0a5809d183b03b78f67afbee6af5c47ae66d3c62","tid":1131660,"uid":4787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"547c7782f829e1811754c0c6f893bc7c97a7dd28","tid":1131660,"uid":247934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T00:20:56.000Z",